<html>
<body>
Reports possible problems caused by non-standard EL extensions:
JSF EL expressions outside attributes, non-standard EL expressions, and so on.

<p><b>Example:</b></p><br/>
<pre><code>
&lt;f:view&gt;
  &lt;h:form&gt;
    &lt;f:loadBundle var="example"/&gt;
    &lt;h:commandButton action="${example.size()}"/&gt; // Warning: method call is nonstandard extension
  &lt;/h:form&gt;
&lt;/f:view&gt;
</code></pre>
</body>
</html>
